! style="background:#a0f0a0" colspan=3 | Designated Shrines
! style="background:#a0f0a0" rowspan=2 | Compilation
|- style="white-space:nowrap;"
! style="background:#a0f0a0; padding-right:2.6em; padding-left:2.6em;" | Shrine Name
